# Sheet 8 — Adversarial ML: Setup & Run Guide (Google Colab)

## Files in this submission

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `adversarial_attack.py` | Main script — exercises 8.4 and 8.5 |
| `sheet8_report.md` | Written answers — exercises 8.1–8.6 |
| `README.md` | This file |

---

## What the script produces

| Output file | Exercise | Contents |
|-------------|----------|---------|
| `8.4_adversarial_examples_<task>.png` | 8.4 | 3 rows × 4 cols: clean \| ε=0.01 \| ε=0.05 \| ε=0.10 |
| `8.5_recall_drop_table.txt` | 8.5 | Clean + adversarial recall per model per ε |
| `8.5_recall_drop_plot.png` | 8.5 | Grouped bar chart of recall |

---

## Drive structure expected

```
MyDrive/MyDataset/
├── 2026/2026/
│   ├── sheet3.zip        ← contains sheet3/dataset.py
│   └── test.zip          ← test split used for 8.4 and 8.5
└── sheet3_results/
    └── checkpoints/
        ├── pedestrian.pt
        ├── traffic_light.pt
        └── vehicle.pt
```

